{"tid":979421,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"網上識人比人呃","createTime":"2019-01-12T16:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T16:26:51.000Z","uid":90315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"db6523738e64761a68b378ff8ea033a7ffeadd33","tid":979421,"uid":90315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"&quot;前幾天，<br />\n我在網路 認識ㄧ個小鮮肉.<br />\n運動型、英俊、性感...<br />\n網路聊天後 覺得十分投緣.<br />\n<br />\n他約我 去他家.<br />\n他說：<br />\n我男朋友 明天出差.<br />\n<br />\n我很謹慎.<br />\n問說：<br />\n你男朋友 會不會忽然回來？<br />\n<br />\n小鮮肉說：不會.<br />\n萬一回來了.<br />\n你就說：<br />\n你是清潔公司的人.<br />\n公司 派你來 做清潔.<br />\n擦玻璃什麼的.<br />\n反正快過年了.<br />\n我男朋友 不會懷疑.<br />\n<br />\n結果<br />\n今天 我到小鮮肉家裡.<br />\n好巧不巧. 好死不死.<br />\n才剛坐下來 要喝白開水.<br />\n他男朋友 就回來了.<br />\n他的手 我都還沒有碰到.<br />\n<br />\n我只好 默默的.<br />\n擦了一上午的玻璃.<br />\n還 洗廁所. 洗浴室&hellip;<br />\n他男朋友 在旁邊 指導我作工.<br />\n<br />\n臨走時. <br />\n他男朋友問：多少錢？<br />\n他說：已經付給公司了.<br />\n<br />\n一回家的路上.<br />\n我愈想愈不對勁&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n新的詐騙手法.<br />\n各位要小心...&quot;"},{"pid":"74bcd71404a89a2dc6347eeb46a4cdf7c2b05ca2","tid":979421,"uid":171124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:21:05.000Z","msg":"傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa12d6ff524b9a1e27e2a86cb03e411fe774fd4","tid":979421,"uid":215509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"This is...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4665ef7495bc7faf5c57bb6479cbf06387b293","tid":979421,"uid":217940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:23:39.000Z","msg":"睇過啦  網上炒人嘅"},{"pid":"7d0c51e7e18afcd57fd9959e2307df981acef76c","tid":979421,"uid":90315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d4665ef7495bc7faf5c57bb6479cbf06387b293","tid":979421,"uid":217940,"